			<p><strong>We will help you gain confidence</strong> in your daily life as you work through our training program as well as increasing your overall fitness and strength.   Our coaching allows everyone to learn at their own pace.
			</p>
			<p>Sessions are 1 hour long.  You'll be guided through simple and effective self-defence techniques and live scenario drills in a safe environment.
			</p>
			<p>You'll learn physical skills you need to protect yourself and your legal rights to self-defence in the UK.</p>
			</p>
