			<h2>What will I learn?</h2>

			<p>
				You will learn both the soft skills (your preparation) and the physical skills of self-defence to also include pre-emptive strikes, live-scenario drills and drills to help train your fight, flight or freeze response to fear. 
			</p>
			<h3 class="h4">I'm new to any martial arts training, can i join?</h3>
			<p>
				Yes! If you have no previous experience you are going to learn the fundamentals of martial arts, so you have a foundation of martial knowledge to build upon.  These fundamentals include, strikes (punches, palm strikes, elbows, kicks, knees), stand up clinch, takedowns and the basics of floor fighting. You will also learn simple yet effective footwork, and how to generate striking power. All at your own pace. 
			</p>
			<h3 class="h4">I've got martial arts training experience, is this class for me?</h3>
			<p>
